sense.gloss: to be vacant, to be available, to be free
to have been opened (of one's eyes, mouth, etc.)
to have a hole, to form a gap, to have an interval (between events)

sdata.j: もう↑電話↑↓でんわ↓を↑切↑↓き↓らなくてはなりません。↑電話↑↓でんわ↓が|↑空↑↓す↓く|のを↑待↑↓ま↓っている↑人↑↓ひと↓がいるのです。
sdata.e: I've got to hang up now. Someone is waiting to use the phone.

sdata.j: あと１０↑分↑↓ふん↓で↑手↑↓て↓が|↑空↑↓す↓く|。
sdata.e: I will be free in ten minutes.

sdata.j: ただいま↑満席↑↓まんせき↓です。↑席↑↓せき↓が|↑空↑↓あ↓く|までこちらでお↑待↑↓ま↓ちください。
sdata.e: We are full now. Please wait here until there is a seat.
